'''Alice Rwema''' ni umunyamategeko akaba n'umukozi wa Leta mu [[Rwanda]], kuva muri Kanama 2014, yabaye umuyobozi wungirije w'inama y'ubutegetsi muri Rwanda Energy Group (REG), isosiyete ikora ibijyanye no kubyara ingufu, gutanga amasoko, gukwirakwiza no kohereza mu mahanga ibijyanye n'amashanyarazi. <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20190714050210/http://reg.rw/index.php/about-us/board-of-directors</ref> Kuva muri Gicurasi 2017, yabaye n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ikigo cya REG. <ref name="Link">https://www.linkedin.com/in/alice-rwema-3240697a/?trk=public-profile-join-page</ref>

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Yize muri [[Kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda|kaminuza nkuru yu Rwanda]] ari naho yakuye impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor of Laws mu 2009. Muri 2014, yahawe impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu by'amategeko, inzobere mu bucuruzi mpuzamahanga, imisoro n'ubucuruzi, yakuye muri [[kaminuza y'u Rwanda]] .  Mu mwaka wa 2013, yoherejwe mu kigo cy’amategeko mpuzamahanga cya Ashurst LLP mu gihe cy’amezi atatu, yatewe inkunga n’abavoka mpuzamahanga bo muri [[Afurika]] ndetse na gahunda mpuzamahanga yo mu [[Bwongereza]] ikorera mu [[Bwongereza]] ireberera abunganizi mu mategeko muri [[Afurika]]. <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20171013120606/http://www.ilfa.org.uk/ilfa-lawyers</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Rwema yabaye umujyanama mu by'amategeko muri [[Ministry of Infrastructure (Rwanda) - MININFRA|Minisiteri y'Ibikorwa Remezo]] mu [[Rwanda]] (Mininfra) kuva muri Gicurasi 2009 kugeza 2013. Kuva mu 2013 kugeza muri Mata 2017, yari umujyanama w’ubucuruzi muri minisitiri w’igihugu ishinzwe ingufu n’amazi muri minisiteri y'ishinzwe ibikorwaremezo,  . 

Muri Kanama 2014, yagizwe umuyobozi wungirije wa Rwanda Energy Group Limited, isosiyete ikora ibijyanye na Energy Utility Corporation Limited na Limited Development Company Limited. Kuva muri Gicurasi 2017, yabaye umunyamabanga w'ikigo cya Rwanda Energy Group. Mbere, yari umwe mu bagize inama y’ikigo gishinzwe ingufu n’isuku EWSA. 

== Ibindi bitekerezo ==
Bitewe n'ubuhanga afite mu bijyanye n'amasezerano n'ubucuruzi, yari umujyanama mu by'amategeko muri guverinoma y'u Rwanda mu gihe cyo gutanga isoko ryo kubaka [[Ikibuga muzamahanga cy'indege cya Bugesera|ikibuga cy'indege mpuzamahanga cya Bugesera]]  ubu kirimo kubakwa. <ref>https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/rwanda/Business/Construction-work-on-Bugesera-Airport-starts-/1433224-4056862-gys2md/index.html</ref> Ni n'umuterankunga mu bipimo ngenderwaho bigenga ingufu zirambye, Banki y'isi ifatanya na banki ishinzwe iterambere ry’ingufu zirambye ku rwego mpuzamahanga. <ref>http://rise.esmap.org/contributors/204</ref> Rwema azi neza [[ikinyarwanda]], [[Igiswahili|Igiswahiri]], [[Icyongereza]] [[Igifaransa|n'Igifaransa]] . <ref name="Link" />

